name: Married with Secrets
overview: Rivaling fictional blockbusters like "Girl on a Train" and "Gone Girl," Investigation Discovery's "Married With Secrets" looks at when happily ever after goes horribly wrong. The series dramatizes the twisted psychological warfare of marriages, telling stories of seemingly perfect unions that turn nightmarish after husbands and wives embark on secret lives that take them down devastating paths. From secret sadomasochistic sex games to hit men for hire, there's no vow too sacred to break and no place too twisted to go for these spouses. And once skeletons come out of the closet, no one is safe.

episodes.name: Dr. Deception
episodes.overview: When Jean Claude Dominique is the victim of a hit-and-run, his wife Eliette rushes to his side. It's there she comes face-to-face with his OTHER wife. It's her first glimpse into his double life that leads to her fighting for her own.

episodes.name: Cold Blue Blood
episodes.overview: Dr. Dirk Greineder is one of the most respected men in the upper class community of Wellesley, MA... that is, until a secret X-rated addiction spirals out of control and results in a gruesome murder no one saw coming.

episodes.name: Yes, Master
episodes.overview: When an aspiring kindergarten teacher in Dublin, Ireland goes missing, her family assumes depression over her mother's death drove her to suicide. They never suspected the real reason - involving a twisted BDSM master gone horribly wrong.

episodes.name: A Darker Shade of Blue
episodes.overview: Chaos ensues in Fox Lake, IL, when an officer is found dead. With a potential cop killer on the loose, the town is on lockdown. But when sordid details of the dead officer's secret life come out, the case takes a surprising turn.

episodes.name: Fear the Ether Man
episodes.overview: A serial rapist known as the Ether Man lurks in the shadows of Albuquerque, NM. Victims can't identify the masked attacker and worse still, it looks like he's expanding his hunting grounds. Can anyone stop him before it's too late?

episodes.name: Fatal Fixation
episodes.overview: When Ignacio Garraus meets Shawna Nelson, there's instant heat - despite them both being married to other people. While he's just looking for a good time, she's falling in love. So when he tries to end things for his wife... things take a very dark turn.

episodes.name: Obsession Has Its Price
episodes.overview: Bill Douglas is a respected doctor at Tufts University in Boston. But his focus isn't on science - it's on a bombshell prostitute he met in a red light district called the Combat Zone. Together, they lead double lives... leading to someone's murder.

episodes.name: The Mastermind
episodes.overview: LAPD investigators are on the hunt for a criminal stealing expensive yachts, but what they find instead is a mild mannered man among their own ranks... who's involved in a lot more than just boat theft.

episodes.name: Never Coming Home
episodes.overview: A mother and her two young sons vanish in rural Wyoming, prompting a nationwide search. Leads dry up and the case goes cold... until the revelation of a dark secret leads police to a homicide.

episodes.name: Gambling With Death
episodes.overview: Ernest and Charlene Scherer are found beaten and stabbed to death in their exclusive Northern California community. Police believe it was a robbery gone wrong until investigators hone in on the motive and learn about the killer's twisted double life.

episodes.name: She Loves Me Not
episodes.overview: When Special Forces Major David Shannon is fatally shot in his family home in Fayetteville, NC, investigators  wonder if his job made him a target.

episodes.name: The Man with Two Faces
episodes.overview: Bloomington, IL, Sergeant Jeff Pelo is a respected police officer and, at home, he's a model father and husband. When he's caught trespassing after midnight on a young woman's property, his spotless reputation comes under fire.

episodes.name: Two-Faced
episodes.overview: The decomposed body of a San Francisco businessman is found floating in the California Aqueduct in Tracy, CA. Investigators initially suspect a family member, but without evidence, the case goes cold and It takes detectives several decades to find the real killer.

episodes.name: Serial Deception
episodes.overview: When dozens of women vanish from the Sunshine State in the late '60s, the get filed as presumed runways; police discover the bodies of two missing teens, uncovering the sadistic work of a prolific serial killer.

episodes.name: Missing in Alaska
episodes.overview: Mike Dixiano is heartbroken when his wife, Angela, dies from organ failure after a lifelong battle with drugs and alcohol. While friends and family grieve Angela's death, investigators can't find a death certificate and begin to suspect her husband.

episodes.name: Sick and Twisted
episodes.overview: Dana MacKay is found beaten to death while her husband is out of town and the prime suspect is a woman who has been stalking MacKay for a month's time. Then, an X-rated text message comes to light to unravel the mystery.

episodes.name: The Girl in the Window
episodes.overview: In Arkansas, Lisa Bradford lives a quiet life with her husband, Dennis, and their two young children, then the police arrive on their doorstep to make a revelation so heinous it rips their marriage apart.
